*Period covered: December 11, 2025 to February 25, 2026*

## Executive summary

We started this engagement on December 11, 2025 with nothing: no website, no content, no domain authority. The goal was to build an editorially independent publication, Cash Flow Desk, that AI engines would treat as a credible third-party source and use to surface Ramp in high-intent prompts where Ramp.com was not being cited directly. Within one week the site was live and the first articles were published. Within five weeks, Cash Flow Desk was being cited by Google AI Mode, Perplexity, ChatGPT, Gemini, and Copilot. By the end of the period, domain authority had gone from 0 to 6, 65 articles were indexed, new articles were being cited within 1 day of publication, and Ramp was appearing in AI-generated answers across every major engine for prompts about expense management, corporate cards, and competitor alternatives. In many cases, Ramp appeared in AI answers solely because of Cash Flow Desk's citation.

