- Track citation speed for every new article to keep refining the publish-to-citation pipeline
- Continue testing fan-out posts and gather enough data to make a call on whether to scale them up, adjust the approach, or shift more effort back to long-form
- Build out additional internal linking as the content library grows
- Optimize for broader, more general prompts (e.g., "best expense management software") per the team's stated goals

